\begin_layout Standard
18FR-RCE is a re-development and extension of 18FR, itself a re-development
 and extension of 1830.
 Core changes include a ninth company, an extended train roster (5-trains
 rust), an extended tile-mix, and a reduced bank-size.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section*
Setup
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
18FR-RCE relies on the track-tiles from 1830.
 No other 1830 components are required.
 From 1830's track-tiles, discard the NYC and B tiles (Baltimore & Boston)
 and add 18FR-RCE's additional tiles.
 All other components are supplied by 18FR-RCE.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Place one of the three port markers from 18FR-RCE on the anchor symbol beside
 each of the ports on the map (Bordeaux, Le Havre and Marseilles).
 Otherwise setup the game as you would any other 18xx game.
\end_layout

